quran[6{c,v,t}:
59,4,yeh is liye ke unhon ne khuda aur is ke rasool ki mukhalfat ki. aur jo shakhs khuda ki mukhalfat kere to khuda sakht azaab dainay wala hai
59,5,( momino ) khajoor ke jo darakht tum ne kaat daaley ya un ko apni jaroon par khara rehne diya so khuda ke hukum se tha aur maqsood yeh tha ke woh na farmanoon ko ruswa kere
59,6,aur jo ( maal ) khuda ne apne paighambar ko un logon se ( baghair larai bhraai ke ) dlwaya hai is mein tumhara kuch haq nahi kyunkay is ke liye nah tum ne ghoray doraye nah oont lekin khuda apne payghambaroon ko jin par chahta hai musallat kardaita hai. aur khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
59,7,jo maal khuda ne apne paighambar ko dehaat walon se dlwaya hai woh khuda ke aur paighambar ke aur ( paighambar ke ) qaraabat walon ke aur yatimon ke aur hajatmandon ke aur musafiron ke liye hai. taakay jo log tum mein doulat mand hain un hi ke hathon mein nah phirta rahay. so jo cheez tum ko paighambar den woh le lau. aur jis se mana karen ( is se ) baz raho. aur khuda se drtay raho. be shak khuda sakht azaab dainay wala hai
59,8,( aur ) un muflisaan tarik ul watan ke liye bhi jo apne gharon aur malon se kharij ( aur judda ) kar diye gay hain ( aur ) khuda ke fazl aur is ki khushnodi ke tallab-gaar aur khuda aur is ke paighambar ke madadgaar hain. yahi log sachey ( imandaar ) hain
59,9,aur ( un logon ke liye bhi ) jo muhajreen se pehlay ( hijrat ke ) ghar ( yani madeeney ) mein muqeem aur imaan mein ( mustaqil ) rahay ( aur ) jo log hijrat karkay un ke paas atay hain un se mohabbat karte hain aur jo kuch un ko mila is se apne dil mein kuch khwahish ( aur khalish ) nahi paate aur un ko apni jaanun se muqaddam rakhtay hain khuwa un ko khud ehtiaaj hi ho. aur jo shakhs hiras nafs se bacha liya gaya to aisay log morad panay walay hain
